[Amit Varma]: light reading is horrible no it's just Twitter can be so horrible sometimes

01:10:21.560 --> 01:10:26.760
[Amit Varma]: when you know I mean for people who sort of want to be generally straightforward

01:10:26.760 --> 01:10:30.040
[Amit Varma]: so you know what we've chatted for more than an hour about your personal life

01:10:30.040 --> 01:10:33.360
[Amit Varma]: and we'll quickly do a little bit more of it after the break and then we'll go

01:10:33.360 --> 01:10:37.880
[Amit Varma]: on to the food but for the moment let's now take a quick commercial break and if

