[Amit Varma]: stop quote although I would never advise any of my students to be so lax with

01:24:14.440 --> 01:24:18.640
[Amit Varma]: deadlines but I am I'm terrible with them I like that quote though I love

01:24:18.640 --> 01:24:25.120
[Amit Varma]: that quote yeah it's I think I quoted Adams in the last episode as well which

01:24:25.120 --> 01:24:28.200
[Amit Varma]: makes it seem like I'm some kind of Adams fanboy and I'm actually not but

01:24:28.200 --> 01:24:35.040
[Amit Varma]: these are great quotes though I'm not a hater either so so to kind of get back

